{"tid":401641,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好鐘意聞火柴味？","createTime":"2017-09-15T18:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T08:16:45.000Z","uid":92771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"85fad2dd21d0eff244ba2e84b6dcd4266892b23f","tid":401641,"uid":92771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:28:49.000Z","msg":"我會周不時買定一打火柴返屋企<br />\n「嚓」一聲，<br />\n每次枝火柴點著個下嘅爆發，<br />\n都會令我既驚又喜，仲有「滋滋」嘅著火聲，<br />\n個一下爆發嘅味濃到有d「哽」，<br />\n但係我又覺得好爽好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似成個人醒神晒、打通晒全身經絡咁<br />\n一路燒，一路索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熄左之後仲有d白煙飄飄下、餘香四散⋯<br />\n算唔算怪辟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08183a639d604db5b38ecfce8f32bcf08b88e0e9","tid":401641,"uid":98263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T21:02:31.000Z","msg":"好香，諗起都想聞"},{"pid":"12fcb545c01845be3a46db70b40f7248978722ad","tid":401641,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T21:33:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52cacc2dc5bd80a830823e4d0af9047ae18ec82d","tid":401641,"uid":92771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:31:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>火藥味</blockquote><br />\n係咩火藥？"},{"pid":"5932f2b7c93faaf314cdbc1e82610105de1f8a02","tid":401641,"uid":145238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"巴打有無木香嘅火柴推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}